  "body": "This PR tracks the overall progress on improving and standardizing Prysm cache.\r\n\r\nWorking items:\r\n\r\n- [x] Remove the deprecated caches (i.e. total balance, start shard, seed) #3584 \r\n- [x] Can retrieve shuffled committee indices by inputting state and epoch #3605\r\n- [x] Can cache for shuffled committee indices #3607\r\n- [x] Can update committee cache in block processing #3617\r\n- [x] Use a feature flag #3619\r\n- [x] Make use of the committee cache in helper functions #3625 \r\n- [x] Enhance cache for active validator indices #3629\r\n- [x] Deprecate active indices, shuffled indices and active count caches for the newly implemented committee cache #3631\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nReference doc:  https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1I9ToaccGX-arYoojzexpj3x22qTsoxsnTT8yUyH-kHY/edit#slide=id.p",
